ounding medium, and shows an increased departure from\ngrowth/collapse symmetry close to the bubble; all of these effects are\nmagnified in the stiffer gel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 22:07:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-01"}
