ome under the rule as a risk\nfunction. Finally, we apply the ODTR SuperLearner to the \"Interventions\" study,\nan ongoing randomized controlled trial, to identify which justice-involved\nadults with mental illness benefit most from cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT)\nto reduce criminal re-offending.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 00:05:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Jul 2021 01:27:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 Oct 2021 13:56:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
