 X-ray hardness with\nspectral subtype among O stars is primarily an absorption effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 22:33:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 Oct 2021 00:32:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
